WEBVTT

00:22.710 --> 00:23.280
Sir.

00:28.280 --> 00:28.960
May I ask

00:29.670 --> 00:31.270
if can you cure blood stasis?

00:32.470 --> 00:34.030
If Xiao Wuyi dies,

00:34.150 --> 00:36.110
you can take back
the military power he holds.

00:36.110 --> 00:37.600
Why bother to save his life?

00:37.600 --> 00:39.000
I just want to defeat him,

00:39.200 --> 00:40.350
not to let him perish at my hands.

00:40.350 --> 00:41.880
I can save him.

00:42.320 --> 00:43.600
But if saving him

00:43.600 --> 00:45.330
is at the cost of others' lives,

00:45.710 --> 00:48.110
can you bear the weight of such a sin?

00:51.200 --> 00:51.960
Yes.

00:52.640 --> 00:53.900
I once saved your life.

00:54.560 --> 00:57.110
In return, you promised
to save three people for me.

00:57.110 --> 00:57.790
The first one...

00:57.790 --> 00:58.710
The first one

00:58.840 --> 01:00.960
was the young emperor.

01:01.150 --> 01:02.200
I did save him.

01:02.200 --> 01:03.960
He is still alive now.

01:06.280 --> 01:07.540
Then the second person

01:08.400 --> 01:10.330
I'm asking you to save is Xiao Wuyi.

02:38.020 --> 02:41.970
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:42.210 --> 02:44.950
[Episode 24]

03:04.000 --> 03:05.330
It never crossed my mind

03:05.520 --> 03:06.780
that you would help me.

03:09.250 --> 03:10.020
I believe...

03:11.560 --> 03:13.820
Mother would also agree to let me do this.

03:17.030 --> 03:17.630
Right.

03:19.470 --> 03:20.560
Neither did I expect

03:20.560 --> 03:23.090
Xiao Wuyi to put righteousness
above family,

03:23.310 --> 03:24.570
reopen the An-Lu case,

03:25.280 --> 03:27.120
and even tell the whole world

03:27.710 --> 03:29.510
that Crown Prince Wenxi is dead,

03:29.680 --> 03:31.360
thus leaving himself no way out.

03:31.360 --> 03:32.360
It seems he really

03:34.680 --> 03:36.610
doesn't care about that position.

03:38.800 --> 03:40.750
All the people in this world pray for

03:40.750 --> 03:42.610
nothing but peace and happiness.

03:42.800 --> 03:44.560
Who cares if the throne is made

03:44.870 --> 03:45.870
of gold or bronze?

03:47.520 --> 03:49.360
I truly look forward to the Ye

03:50.400 --> 03:52.060
that Xiao Wuyi tries to build,

03:52.360 --> 03:54.090
and I'm glad to help him with it.

04:08.240 --> 04:09.030
Yaoyao.

04:14.400 --> 04:15.530
As your father, I...

04:30.950 --> 04:34.560
I did much wrongdoing in the past.

04:36.930 --> 04:38.680
I must apologize to you.

04:42.170 --> 04:43.409
I am so sorry.

04:49.240 --> 04:51.640
It's cold and harsh
in the Northern Border.

04:53.830 --> 04:54.560
Do take care

04:56.870 --> 04:58.560
to stay warm.

05:07.630 --> 05:08.430
Fuhua,

05:15.360 --> 05:16.870
you had a good daughter.

05:23.120 --> 05:26.270
His Majesty has agreed to establish
the spring exam as a regular system.

05:26.270 --> 05:29.200
The Grand Tutor has also submitted
his resignation.

05:30.870 --> 05:32.130
You beat me once again.

05:35.040 --> 05:36.159
When will you go back
to the Northern Border?

05:36.159 --> 05:38.000
I've petitioned His Majesty for leave

05:38.000 --> 05:40.640
to first inspect the capital's defense
in three days before heading back

05:40.640 --> 05:41.750
to the Northern Border.

05:41.750 --> 05:43.870
The Eagle King's troops
have been making moves.

05:43.870 --> 05:45.130
I need to get back soon.

05:45.560 --> 05:46.600
Now, I'm thinking

05:47.510 --> 05:48.909
that you're about to die,

05:49.270 --> 05:50.870
but there is still so much time left

05:50.870 --> 05:52.600
in my life and Xie Jiayu's life.

05:52.800 --> 05:54.130
Anything could happen.

05:55.070 --> 05:55.830
So,

05:57.270 --> 05:58.670
there shouldn't be rush.

06:07.390 --> 06:10.500
The mystery of mineral deposits
within the Phoenix Heart Token

06:10.500 --> 06:12.160
has been cracked by Xie Jiayu.

06:12.750 --> 06:14.500
If the court needs them in the future,

06:14.500 --> 06:16.230
she'll tell you where they are.

06:16.950 --> 06:18.210
With Xie Jiayu around,

06:19.560 --> 06:20.630
this token

06:22.920 --> 06:24.050
is no longer useful.

06:30.720 --> 06:31.320
Xiao Wuyi!

06:34.920 --> 06:37.120
"When the Phoenix Heart Token appears,
peace shall be restored in the world."

06:37.120 --> 06:38.750
You didn't hesitate to destroy

06:38.750 --> 06:40.010
what others yearn for.

06:41.060 --> 06:42.430
By replacing the token with Xie Jiayu,

06:42.430 --> 06:44.870
you're trying to make sure
no one can hurt her

06:44.870 --> 06:46.530
whether you are alive or dead,

06:48.510 --> 06:49.360
not even me.

06:50.800 --> 06:52.330
You devised a thorough plan

06:52.680 --> 06:54.010
and gave up everything,

06:54.040 --> 06:55.270
yet in the final days of your life,

06:55.270 --> 06:57.200
you chose to leave her and go to war.

06:57.800 --> 06:59.680
Xiao Wuyi, what on earth

07:00.430 --> 07:01.310
matters most

07:02.120 --> 07:03.040
to you?

07:16.480 --> 07:17.940
Please don't die too soon.

07:18.680 --> 07:20.210
I will surely beat you once.

07:35.070 --> 07:35.750
Xiao Wuyi!

07:38.720 --> 07:39.690
Li Mao has gone back to the palace.

07:39.690 --> 07:40.750
Let's go home, too.

07:45.970 --> 07:46.900
Why is it broken?

07:49.880 --> 07:51.680
This is the Phoenix Heart Token.

07:52.310 --> 07:54.270
You already know it by heart, don't you?

07:54.270 --> 07:55.670
What use does it have now?

07:57.070 --> 07:57.830
Besides,

07:58.190 --> 08:01.120
it was originally my mother's
Phoenix Imperial Seal.

08:01.120 --> 08:02.780
How about we melt it and cast it

08:02.830 --> 08:04.090
into a hairpin for you?

08:08.470 --> 08:11.080
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

08:17.390 --> 08:19.070
Yuanji, you're so full of surprises.

08:19.070 --> 08:21.800
You got the first place
in the exam in just one try.

08:29.040 --> 08:31.950
I thought the most nervous moment
of my life would be the day

08:31.950 --> 08:34.280
I married into Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

08:34.600 --> 08:35.659
Little did I expect

08:35.730 --> 08:38.130
to feel even more nervous
now than that day.

08:39.320 --> 08:41.120
That said, I've never been so clear

08:41.120 --> 08:42.600
about my goal as I am today.

08:44.440 --> 08:46.840
But I'm a bit worried about your identity.

08:47.600 --> 08:49.200
If Mao ever...

08:49.270 --> 08:50.960
Yaoyao, you're worried about nothing.

08:50.960 --> 08:51.670
Prince Qi

08:51.670 --> 08:53.870
was even more eager than I was
about the exam results.

08:53.870 --> 08:55.440
Since he didn't expose my identity,

08:55.440 --> 08:57.320
I'm sure he won't either in the future.

08:57.320 --> 08:58.690
Only when he has some kind of hold on me

08:58.690 --> 09:00.550
will he feel more at ease using me.

09:03.950 --> 09:06.790
[Zhuque Gate]

09:26.470 --> 09:31.620
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

09:32.910 --> 09:38.490
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

09:39.150 --> 09:45.450
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

09:41.250 --> 09:44.270
I deem it as a blessing for me
to marry into the Xiao family,

09:44.270 --> 09:45.720
to become part of the household,

09:45.720 --> 09:52.200
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

09:45.910 --> 09:47.640
and to support each other here.

09:48.030 --> 09:50.030
You'll be embraced by the vast world.

09:50.030 --> 09:50.630
I wish you

09:51.120 --> 09:52.120
all the best,

09:52.710 --> 09:58.130
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong? ♪

09:53.550 --> 09:55.410
and may all your dreams come true.

09:58.730 --> 10:04.110
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

10:04.900 --> 10:08.550
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

10:08.650 --> 10:11.100
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

10:11.330 --> 10:17.350
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

10:17.630 --> 10:21.180
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

10:21.200 --> 10:24.170
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

10:24.200 --> 10:29.680
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

10:56.870 --> 10:58.530
Where are you going, Darling?

11:03.960 --> 11:04.890
Three years ago,

11:05.150 --> 11:06.480
you fled to Northern Qin

11:06.720 --> 11:08.180
and begged me for shelter,

11:08.560 --> 11:10.480
saying that you offended Xiao Wuyi

11:10.480 --> 11:13.120
and even your brother, the Regent,
couldn't protect you,

11:13.120 --> 11:14.440
so you were driven out of Southern Ye

11:14.440 --> 11:15.670
to fend for yourself.

11:17.150 --> 11:17.750
What now?

11:18.630 --> 11:20.720
You want to return to your homeland?

11:21.150 --> 11:22.810
Do you not fear death anymore?

11:25.080 --> 11:27.030
Isn't there a saying in Southern Ye?

11:27.030 --> 11:29.230
That is, "Once a couple, always a bond."

11:29.270 --> 11:31.400
Can you really bear to leave me behind?

11:33.600 --> 11:34.600
Don't you forget

11:35.280 --> 11:37.830
that I've never intercepted
a single letter

11:38.550 --> 11:39.930
you've sent to Jiankang in secret

11:39.930 --> 11:42.590
after collecting intelligence
in the Capital.

11:43.240 --> 11:45.440
What discontent can you possibly have?

11:46.270 --> 11:48.080
So you've been using me.

11:49.440 --> 11:52.000
All you've done is for today, right?

11:53.750 --> 11:54.630
I just presented

11:54.630 --> 11:56.550
a great opportunity to your brother.

11:56.550 --> 11:58.080
You should be thanking me.

12:00.630 --> 12:02.960
For that injustice from over 20 years ago,

12:03.270 --> 12:04.800
it is time to put an end to it.

12:05.270 --> 12:09.000
After all, your brother is a descendant
of the Xie family, isn't he?

12:09.150 --> 12:09.840
Guards!

12:10.390 --> 12:11.200
Take her away.

12:11.720 --> 12:12.380
-Yes.
-Yes.

12:22.630 --> 12:25.320
[Post House, Guazhou]

12:33.270 --> 12:34.600
By order of the Heir's Consort,

12:34.600 --> 12:35.940
Your Highness must not
strain your eyes anymore.

12:35.940 --> 12:37.050
You think you run the place,

12:37.050 --> 12:38.390
now that someone's backing you up?

12:38.390 --> 12:39.920
I'm just following orders.

12:40.480 --> 12:41.490
If Your Highness is angry,

12:41.490 --> 12:43.020
take it out on Her Highness.

12:45.670 --> 12:47.320
It's noticeable in this inspection
of the capital's defense

12:47.320 --> 12:48.270
that the Imperial Guard's
combat power has improved.

12:48.270 --> 12:49.670
The reform has proven effective,

12:49.670 --> 12:51.340
and removed the potential risks
of the Northern Expedition.

12:51.340 --> 12:53.270
Why are you still worried, Your Highness?

12:53.270 --> 12:54.360
I don't like war,

12:55.140 --> 12:57.340
but peace can't be restored without it.

12:57.790 --> 12:59.870
Whether a nation prospers or falls,

13:00.600 --> 13:02.530
it is always the people who suffer.

13:06.200 --> 13:08.160
From now on, you are no longer
registered as a slave,

13:08.160 --> 13:10.390
but the manager of the Miraculous Craft.

13:10.390 --> 13:11.440
I'm leaving you to handle everything

13:11.440 --> 13:12.500
I have in Jiankang.

13:14.240 --> 13:15.970
Ever since Cang'er's passing,

13:16.070 --> 13:18.270
I've been considering your placement.

13:18.670 --> 13:20.360
Good thing you didn't fall in love
with Qing Long.

13:20.360 --> 13:21.390
Otherwise, I would be worried

13:21.390 --> 13:22.750
if I had to marry you to a man who could

13:22.750 --> 13:23.960
get on the battlefield anytime.

13:23.960 --> 13:25.480
There's no way I'd be into him.

13:25.480 --> 13:27.630
But I can see
he clings to you all the time.

13:27.630 --> 13:28.960
He's not clinging to me.

13:29.240 --> 13:30.320
He's clearly trying to spend

13:30.320 --> 13:32.180
more time with Yan Yue through me.

13:32.250 --> 13:33.380
Then what about you?

13:33.390 --> 13:36.050
I also love being around
with Yan Yue, of course.

13:36.390 --> 13:37.480
In my heart,

13:37.720 --> 13:38.520
Your Highness

13:38.800 --> 13:40.060
is the most important.

13:41.030 --> 13:42.830
I wish to stick with you, My Lady.

13:44.200 --> 13:45.080
You silly girl.

13:45.240 --> 13:46.440
I just entrusted you

13:46.440 --> 13:47.440
with my biggest fallback.

13:47.440 --> 13:49.670
You're highly talented
in business and accounting.

13:49.670 --> 13:50.670
Both warfare

13:50.670 --> 13:51.960
and weapon manufacturing

13:51.960 --> 13:53.420
cost a great deal of money.

13:53.910 --> 13:55.080
If I am short of money in the future

13:55.080 --> 13:56.320
and write to you for help,

13:56.320 --> 13:58.180
you must not pretend not to see it.

13:58.600 --> 13:59.530
I swear, My Lady,

13:59.750 --> 14:01.750
to manage the Miraculous Craft well

14:01.790 --> 14:03.320
and make more money for you.

14:09.360 --> 14:11.210
Master, are you sure about
sending all these books

14:11.210 --> 14:12.610
to the Imperial Academy?

14:13.390 --> 14:14.190
You've gone to

14:14.240 --> 14:16.700
great lengths to collect them
all your life.

14:18.320 --> 14:20.050
Now that I'm letting things go,

14:20.960 --> 14:22.690
I might as well do it all the way.

14:25.360 --> 14:26.720
Master, do you really think

14:26.720 --> 14:28.780
His Highness chose the correct path?

14:29.910 --> 14:30.790
Jiayu...

14:34.240 --> 14:36.750
Yaoyao said something right.

14:38.240 --> 14:40.750
Each generation has its own path to walk.

14:42.080 --> 14:44.440
Now, Yizhi is sure to ascend the throne.

14:45.360 --> 14:46.910
Although the path he will take

14:46.910 --> 14:47.970
may not be correct,

14:48.550 --> 14:51.150
sticking to old patterns is surely wrong.

14:53.600 --> 14:54.750
As for us...

14:57.720 --> 14:59.440
As for us old folks,

15:00.360 --> 15:02.510
it's time we made way for them.

15:05.750 --> 15:06.510
Grand Tutor!

15:08.630 --> 15:10.760
Can you really bear to leave Jiankang?

15:12.910 --> 15:13.840
Prince Jing'an?

15:14.080 --> 15:15.340
Are you really going to

15:15.480 --> 15:17.480
let me and my family off the hook
so easily?

15:17.480 --> 15:18.410
What do you mean?

15:20.000 --> 15:21.000
I wrote

15:21.360 --> 15:23.870
this confession to Empress Wenxi myself.

15:24.870 --> 15:26.790
Grand Tutor, don't you want to know

15:26.790 --> 15:27.790
who orchestrated

15:28.960 --> 15:30.200
that injustice

15:30.910 --> 15:32.390
from years ago?

15:33.790 --> 15:34.590
Aren't you...

15:35.270 --> 15:36.080
Master!

16:22.670 --> 16:23.730
Someone come here!

16:26.240 --> 16:27.170
Is anyone there?

16:28.960 --> 16:31.000
How odd. Why is no one around?

16:32.510 --> 16:33.120
Mother!

16:34.360 --> 16:35.320
Ruisheng!

16:35.790 --> 16:36.550
Father!

16:37.270 --> 16:39.930
Did Father go out for drinks
and gambling again?

16:40.790 --> 16:42.790
Prince Qi invites Your Highness

16:42.960 --> 16:44.240
to the Grand Tutor's Mansion.

16:43.890 --> 16:46.080
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

16:46.550 --> 16:47.150
Yaoyao.

16:49.080 --> 16:51.080
Please don't cry
when you see the Grand Tutor later.

16:51.080 --> 16:52.600
Though he had selfish motives before,

16:52.600 --> 16:54.460
he did spend 18 years raising you.

16:55.000 --> 16:56.600
Death wipes away all wrongs.

16:57.170 --> 16:58.630
So don't hate him anymore.

17:44.060 --> 17:47.480
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

17:47.780 --> 17:51.460
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

17:51.570 --> 17:55.930
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

17:56.290 --> 17:58.990
♪ So desolate ♪

17:56.790 --> 17:58.160
I made this black jade thumb ring

17:58.160 --> 17:59.420
on my own specifically

17:59.480 --> 18:00.790
as a birthday gift to you, Father.

17:59.570 --> 18:03.230
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

18:02.030 --> 18:02.790
What do you think?

18:02.790 --> 18:03.350
Is it pretty?

18:03.260 --> 18:06.800
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

18:04.480 --> 18:05.200
Yes.

18:06.070 --> 18:06.790
So pretty.

18:06.990 --> 18:12.320
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

18:08.640 --> 18:10.830
I'll keep it on all the time,

18:11.350 --> 18:14.200
and think of my dearest Yaoyao
all the time.

18:12.960 --> 18:16.400
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

18:14.750 --> 18:15.310
Great.

18:16.430 --> 18:20.420
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

18:20.560 --> 18:24.270
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

18:24.290 --> 18:28.000
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

18:28.250 --> 18:31.070
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

18:31.090 --> 18:33.580
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

18:33.840 --> 18:38.010
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

18:37.590 --> 18:38.440
Father...

18:38.040 --> 18:41.630
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

18:41.880 --> 18:43.650
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

18:43.880 --> 18:46.500
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

18:46.530 --> 18:49.200
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

18:49.450 --> 18:53.690
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

18:51.310 --> 18:52.310
Father!

18:54.020 --> 18:58.190
♪ I'd bid farewell to every worldly part ♪

18:56.750 --> 18:59.270
The chapter of Jade Algae
in the Book of Rites says:

18:58.500 --> 19:03.340
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

18:59.590 --> 19:02.590
"Keep the voice calm, the head upright,
and the bearing dignified."

19:02.590 --> 19:03.790
Do you remember what it means?

19:03.790 --> 19:04.880
A person of virtue should

19:04.880 --> 19:06.310
behave and speak with composure,

19:06.310 --> 19:08.550
holding his or her head high
when walking and sitting.

19:08.550 --> 19:09.110
Father,

19:09.500 --> 19:11.560
sorry for losing my manners just now.

19:12.820 --> 19:14.530
If you were not my daughter,

19:15.360 --> 19:16.510
you could have

19:18.200 --> 19:19.550
led a freer life.

19:21.300 --> 19:22.140
Father...

19:31.510 --> 19:32.640
How did this happen?

19:34.400 --> 19:35.860
What exactly was going on?

19:36.350 --> 19:37.240
Wasn't he preparing to retire

19:37.240 --> 19:38.770
and return to his hometown?

19:39.200 --> 19:40.750
Who on earth did this?

19:43.860 --> 19:44.660
It was Xiao Ju.

19:49.240 --> 19:50.000
What?

19:51.830 --> 19:52.640
That's impossible.

19:52.640 --> 19:54.840
The Commandant of Justice
and the common people witnessed it.

19:54.840 --> 19:55.600
Xiao Ju

19:55.940 --> 19:57.210
was caught on the spot.

19:59.310 --> 20:00.170
Your Highness!

20:04.350 --> 20:05.400
Say what happened.

20:05.400 --> 20:06.530
Yes, Your Highness.

20:06.640 --> 20:07.510
Heir's Consort,

20:07.510 --> 20:09.830
today, I heard someone causing trouble
in the Grand Tutor's Mansion,

20:09.830 --> 20:10.680
so I came.

20:11.030 --> 20:14.410
Then I ran right into Prince Jing'an
committing a murder here.

20:14.410 --> 20:15.070
Who are you?

20:16.750 --> 20:17.680
Prince Jing'an?

20:21.590 --> 20:23.210
He slashed at everyone he saw as he moved.

20:23.210 --> 20:25.310
All the people on this very street
can testify

20:25.310 --> 20:28.440
that the assailant was exactly
Prince Jing'an, Xiao Ju.

20:29.590 --> 20:31.240
Suddenly, a cart dashed in

20:31.350 --> 20:33.170
and knocked
the fleeing Prince Jing'an down.

20:33.170 --> 20:34.630
Only then was he captured.

20:36.060 --> 20:37.860
All of this seems unreasonable.

20:38.510 --> 20:39.590
If Prince Jing'an wanted revenge

20:39.590 --> 20:40.790
for knowing my father

20:41.200 --> 20:43.000
had conspired with Liu Zhaolin,

20:43.240 --> 20:44.880
he wouldn't have chosen to do it
in broad daylight,

20:44.880 --> 20:46.920
gone out to the street
instead of small alleys

20:46.920 --> 20:48.550
upon being discovered,
or slashed at others.

20:48.550 --> 20:50.070
Wasn't it practically finding witnesses
for himself?

20:50.070 --> 20:51.200
I was also confused,

20:51.440 --> 20:54.790
till I found this
in the Grand Tutor's arms.

21:05.330 --> 21:05.960
This is...

21:06.750 --> 21:09.230
a confession letter Prince Jing'an wrote
to Empress Wenxi years ago.

21:09.230 --> 21:10.250
This confession letter

21:10.250 --> 21:12.110
is dated the 12th year
of the Zhaoning reign,

21:12.110 --> 21:14.370
exactly on the eve of the Capital's fall.

21:14.400 --> 21:16.000
Back then, Prince Jing'an was well aware

21:16.000 --> 21:17.880
that the An and Lu families
were falsely accused,

21:17.880 --> 21:20.440
yet he still brought these 200-odd people
onto the execution ground.

21:20.440 --> 21:22.160
So, when Prince Jing'an learned

21:22.160 --> 21:23.960
that this letter
was in the Grand Tutor's hands,

21:23.960 --> 21:25.240
he killed the latter to silence him.

21:25.240 --> 21:26.700
This makes perfect sense.

21:26.880 --> 21:27.740
It's not right.

21:28.440 --> 21:30.480
My father figured out long ago
that the An and Lu families were wronged.

21:30.480 --> 21:31.720
If he had known about this letter,

21:31.720 --> 21:33.680
he wouldn't have kept silent for so long.

21:33.680 --> 21:34.940
When the Capital fell,

21:35.270 --> 21:37.270
if this letter wasn't ruined at war,

21:37.350 --> 21:39.550
then it must've gone to Northern Qin...

21:39.960 --> 21:40.480
Right.

21:41.030 --> 21:42.090
It's Northern Qin.

21:42.190 --> 21:42.920
Commandant,

21:43.720 --> 21:45.260
did you see Prince Jing'an speak
at that time?

21:45.260 --> 21:46.060
No, he didn't.

21:48.090 --> 21:49.090
That explains it.

21:49.370 --> 21:51.630
One's accent gives away one's identity.

21:53.110 --> 21:54.920
Mao, do you remember Cui Jun?

21:55.480 --> 21:57.240
He used the secret disguise technique
of Northern Qin.

21:57.240 --> 21:59.500
This is all a conspiracy by Northern Qin.

22:11.310 --> 22:12.310
Your Highness...

22:14.680 --> 22:16.720
Who had the audacity to tie me up?

22:17.210 --> 22:18.030
Untie me now!

22:18.030 --> 22:18.960
Prince Jing'an,

22:20.160 --> 22:21.400
what do you have to say?

22:21.400 --> 22:21.960
I...

22:22.100 --> 22:24.050
was on my way home after gambling

22:24.830 --> 22:25.720
when someone attacked me.

22:25.720 --> 22:27.550
Then I woke up and found myself here

22:27.550 --> 22:29.080
without knowing anything.

22:31.880 --> 22:32.750
Your Highness,

22:33.100 --> 22:34.070
Anfeng Restaurant,

22:34.070 --> 22:34.880
Laowang Temple,

22:34.880 --> 22:36.350
Su's Rouge Shop, and four other

22:36.350 --> 22:37.590
spy outposts of Northern Qin

22:37.590 --> 22:39.110
have all been investigated.

22:39.110 --> 22:40.790
The Northern Qin spies
are working as normal,

22:40.790 --> 22:41.830
showing no suspicious activity.

22:41.830 --> 22:43.560
Neither has anyone withdrawn.

22:43.880 --> 22:46.250
If this was really the work
of Northern Qin spies,

22:46.250 --> 22:48.890
logically speaking,
whether it was a success or a failure,

22:48.890 --> 22:50.270
they would've withdrawn instantly.

22:50.270 --> 22:51.530
But they didn't leave.

22:51.880 --> 22:54.240
They must have no knowledge of this,
since they wouldn't

22:54.240 --> 22:56.700
just wait to be rounded up
all at once, right?

22:58.440 --> 22:59.370
Prince Jing'an,

22:59.550 --> 23:00.960
you said someone attacked you.

23:00.960 --> 23:02.090
Was there a witness?

23:02.720 --> 23:03.680
Probably...

23:04.400 --> 23:05.070
no.

23:06.440 --> 23:08.400
When I go gambling,

23:08.480 --> 23:10.480
I always do it behind my wife's back.

23:11.070 --> 23:12.350
But Jiayu knows it.

23:17.310 --> 23:19.910
Is the content
of this confession letter true?

23:22.110 --> 23:23.510
Back then, in order to...

23:24.200 --> 23:25.860
suppress the noble families,

23:26.200 --> 23:26.920
I...

23:28.750 --> 23:30.610
didn't reveal the truth, indeed.

23:34.750 --> 23:37.400
Given that justice has been restored
for the An and Lu families...

23:37.400 --> 23:37.920
Guards!

23:38.480 --> 23:39.140
-Yes!
-Yes!

23:39.550 --> 23:42.070
Detain everyone
in Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

23:42.070 --> 23:44.960
and have Xiao Yao arrested and brought
back from Yingzhou immediately.

23:44.960 --> 23:46.040
Strip him of his post there as well.

23:46.040 --> 23:46.560
Yes.

23:46.790 --> 23:47.690
Your Highness...

23:47.690 --> 23:48.650
The detention will be in secret.

23:48.650 --> 23:49.980
Your Highness, this...

23:50.060 --> 23:50.540
This...

23:51.030 --> 23:53.110
Xiao Wuyi hasn't returned
from the inspection tour yet.

23:53.110 --> 23:55.160
All that has happened here
must be kept secret

23:55.160 --> 23:56.620
from him, in case he flees.

24:01.830 --> 24:04.230
Escort the Heir's Consort into the palace.

24:04.400 --> 24:05.200
Take her away!

24:28.000 --> 24:29.660
Shouldn't you say something?

24:30.510 --> 24:31.680
What should I say?

24:32.310 --> 24:33.640
Mock me, scold me, throw

24:33.750 --> 24:35.150
a tantrum or threaten me.

24:35.240 --> 24:36.240
Anything is fine.

24:36.590 --> 24:38.000
Just do what you used to.

24:40.510 --> 24:42.370
Time passes like a flowing river.

24:42.920 --> 24:45.380
How can you expect things
to remain the same?

24:46.750 --> 24:48.720
Did I turn you into this?

24:49.310 --> 24:51.830
You knew my father's death
was suspicious in many ways,

24:51.830 --> 24:54.070
and that Prince Jing'an was framed
by Northern Qin.

24:54.070 --> 24:55.720
But you still seized on it
to stir up more trouble.

24:55.720 --> 24:57.050
How I wish you were angry

24:58.110 --> 24:59.590
partly because of me.

25:02.880 --> 25:05.140
I thought after the spring examination,

25:05.310 --> 25:07.170
you and Xiao Wuyi had reconciled.

25:07.310 --> 25:09.550
But I'm also afraid you'd only remember
the bad things about me.

25:09.550 --> 25:12.150
You believe
Xiao Wuyi has never coveted power,

25:12.460 --> 25:14.440
and you've obtained
the Phoenix Heart Token.

25:14.440 --> 25:16.900
He can't prove he is Crown Prince Wenxi
by any means.

25:16.900 --> 25:17.560
Besides...

25:18.800 --> 25:20.860
he can't live for much longer anyway.

25:27.640 --> 25:29.970
Don't you resent him for dragging you down

25:30.510 --> 25:31.910
as his days are numbered?

25:33.030 --> 25:34.350
No one can drag me down.

25:37.110 --> 25:39.110
I willingly chose to stick with him.

25:39.880 --> 25:41.540
Then if he leaves you forever,

25:42.240 --> 25:43.170
what will you do?

25:43.960 --> 25:45.820
As long as he has never let me down,

25:47.160 --> 25:48.620
even if he is gone forever,

25:49.240 --> 25:51.100
I'll still feel like he's around.

25:52.510 --> 25:54.000
I'll carry on his legacy

25:55.270 --> 25:56.480
and live my life well.

25:59.720 --> 26:01.520
Does it mean you left me back then

26:02.160 --> 26:03.890
because I somehow let you down?

26:05.000 --> 26:06.800
I just couldn't understand you,

26:09.960 --> 26:10.960
like now—

26:11.880 --> 26:13.110
I still can't tell

26:16.270 --> 26:17.510
when you are acting

26:18.200 --> 26:19.930
and when you are being genuine.

26:27.830 --> 26:28.550
Maybe

26:29.660 --> 26:31.790
you really are suited to be an emperor.

26:32.110 --> 26:33.240
Unpredictable.

26:33.830 --> 26:35.490
Calculated like a sovereign.

26:36.200 --> 26:37.680
How very fearful.

26:44.130 --> 26:44.830
Officers,

26:44.830 --> 26:45.720
I'm terribly sorry.

26:45.720 --> 26:46.780
I'll go right away.

26:50.000 --> 26:50.930
Are you alright?

26:52.400 --> 26:54.400
You keep me in chains yet protect me.

26:54.510 --> 26:55.070
Mao,

26:56.240 --> 26:57.900
you're such a contradiction.

27:01.350 --> 27:03.550
I remember you're allergic to peaches.

27:03.550 --> 27:05.270
Never did I imagine that one day,

27:05.270 --> 27:07.270
I'd have no choice but to attack you.

27:26.160 --> 27:26.830
Freeze!

27:44.270 --> 27:45.070
As you said,

27:45.400 --> 27:46.350
Prince Qi knew that Northern Qin

27:46.350 --> 27:47.590
plotted to turn a ruler
against his ministers,

27:47.590 --> 27:49.270
yet he still capitalized on it to seize

27:49.270 --> 27:51.200
Prince Jing'an's military power.

27:51.250 --> 27:53.880
So he just faked
his previous alliance with Wuyi...

27:53.880 --> 27:55.000
Right now, I have no idea

27:55.000 --> 27:56.350
if he's being genuine or pretending.

27:56.350 --> 27:57.000
The priority

27:57.000 --> 27:58.400
is to have Xiao Wuyi found

27:58.480 --> 28:00.000
and warned not to come back to Jiankang

28:00.000 --> 28:01.030
so he won't fall into this trap.

28:01.030 --> 28:01.830
You're right.

28:02.030 --> 28:03.330
A man is judged by his actions,
not his thoughts,

28:03.330 --> 28:04.590
let alone a sovereign.

28:05.680 --> 28:06.590
I'm afraid only I can

28:06.590 --> 28:08.390
speak up for the Xiao family now.

28:08.750 --> 28:09.790
I'll submit a memorial tomorrow.

28:09.790 --> 28:10.550
Don't, Yuanji.

28:10.550 --> 28:11.790
Or you'll irritate Prince Qi.

28:11.790 --> 28:12.790
An official must be loyal,

28:12.790 --> 28:14.050
but not blindly loyal.

28:14.160 --> 28:15.750
If there are so many doubts
about this case,

28:15.750 --> 28:17.680
then it is my duty
to submit a memorial on it.

28:17.680 --> 28:19.210
You stay here for the night.

28:19.490 --> 28:20.180
Keep up!

28:26.090 --> 28:28.890
Da is leading some Imperial Guards
to look for you.

28:32.070 --> 28:33.270
They are almost here!

28:34.100 --> 28:35.900
Yuanji, lend me the seal
of the Household Department.

28:35.900 --> 28:36.560
No problem.

28:47.160 --> 28:47.890
She ran away,

28:48.240 --> 28:51.100
after robbing me
of the Household Department seal.

29:06.960 --> 29:08.000
Leave town tonight,

29:08.000 --> 29:09.270
and rush to the post house.

29:09.270 --> 29:10.790
Make sure you tell the Heir
about the incident in Jiankang

29:10.790 --> 29:12.270
before Prince Qi's people arrive.

29:12.270 --> 29:12.830
Got it.

29:13.750 --> 29:15.240
However, now, there must be ambushes

29:15.240 --> 29:16.700
all around the city walls.

29:16.920 --> 29:18.250
This time, leaving town

29:18.440 --> 29:19.830
will get you in grave danger.

29:19.830 --> 29:20.830
I alone might not be able

29:20.830 --> 29:21.880
to fight off many soldiers,

29:21.880 --> 29:23.240
but I can definitely outrun them.

29:23.240 --> 29:25.400
There won't be anyone left
for you to use here

29:25.400 --> 29:26.720
once I am out of the city.

29:26.720 --> 29:27.920
As for your safety...

29:29.440 --> 29:30.170
Don't worry.

29:30.720 --> 29:31.450
Who's there?

29:31.590 --> 29:33.450
I'll protect the Heir's Consort.

29:36.920 --> 29:38.570
You're also a royal Shadow Envoy?

29:38.570 --> 29:39.440
Not just me.

29:40.070 --> 29:40.790
In Jiankang,

29:40.790 --> 29:42.450
there are many others like me,

29:42.480 --> 29:43.240
who were ordered

29:43.240 --> 29:44.870
years ago to protect Crown Prince Wenxi.

29:44.870 --> 29:47.400
But Crown Prince Wenxi
has never called on us.

29:47.660 --> 29:49.920
He only hopes that we live our lives well.

29:59.200 --> 29:59.920
Ye Xing?

30:02.640 --> 30:03.500
Your Highness!

30:03.530 --> 30:04.760
Prince Jing'an killed Xie Huaigui
and was caught

30:04.760 --> 30:06.070
by the Commandant of Justice
on the spot!

30:06.070 --> 30:06.880
While being pursued,

30:06.880 --> 30:08.640
Prince Jing'an even severely
injured the Commandant.

30:08.640 --> 30:09.550
Prince Qi has ordered

30:09.550 --> 30:11.370
everyone in the mansion to be detained!

30:11.370 --> 30:13.100
What about the Heir's Consort?

30:17.270 --> 30:18.030
He Yuan,

30:19.110 --> 30:20.840
you are not an imperial censor.

30:20.990 --> 30:22.920
It is not your duty to remonstrate.

30:23.950 --> 30:27.030
Has Your Highness forgotten
about the Northern Expedition?

30:27.030 --> 30:27.880
How insolent!

30:29.070 --> 30:30.880
Do not forget whose salary you take.

30:30.880 --> 30:31.960
I am completely loyal, and I admonish

30:31.960 --> 30:33.310
for the good of the country.

30:33.310 --> 30:35.110
The Xiao family has been
in charge of Beifu for years,

30:35.110 --> 30:37.310
with a distinguished military record
and a credit to the nation.

30:37.310 --> 30:39.550
I hope Your Highness will investigate
the Grand Tutor's death thoroughly,

30:39.550 --> 30:41.200
and not be instigated by Northern Qin

30:41.200 --> 30:43.480
to sow discord
between Your Highness and the Beifu Army,

30:43.480 --> 30:46.010
thus jeopardizing the Northern Expedition.

30:46.270 --> 30:48.270
Such clever yet fallacious remarks

30:48.350 --> 30:49.880
have added to your offense.

30:49.880 --> 30:51.170
Strike him 30 times with a cane

30:51.170 --> 30:52.500
right here in the court.

30:52.550 --> 30:53.160
Yes.

30:53.270 --> 30:54.000
Attendants!

31:15.490 --> 31:17.350
Years ago, when the Capital fell,

31:17.430 --> 31:19.290
countless Ye people were reduced

31:19.830 --> 31:21.290
to slaves of Northern Qin,

31:21.620 --> 31:23.950
living a life
worse than that of an animal.

31:24.510 --> 31:26.640
War has never ceased for 20-odd years.

31:26.640 --> 31:28.350
Now, I have arrested Prince Jing'an

31:28.350 --> 31:30.550
not because of the Grand Tutor's death,

31:31.640 --> 31:34.750
but the purpose of sacrificing
a sinful minister's head

31:34.750 --> 31:36.880
to the upcoming Northern Expedition.

31:38.960 --> 31:40.790
I no longer care if you lot

31:41.400 --> 31:42.640
suspect my identity,

31:43.200 --> 31:44.530
because what I need to do

31:45.430 --> 31:48.670
is let my determination be seen
by all in the world.

32:01.510 --> 32:04.570
Your Highness, a secret report
from the Brocade Guard.

32:21.210 --> 32:21.940
Announce it.

32:22.920 --> 32:26.180
Read it out aloud before the top scholar
of the spring exam.

32:26.610 --> 32:27.200
Yes.

32:28.590 --> 32:30.790
Beacon fires were lit
and an urgent message came from afar:

32:30.790 --> 32:32.400
A Black Cavalry squad of the Beifu Army

32:32.400 --> 32:33.660
is traveling day and night,

32:33.660 --> 32:34.880
heading straight for Jiankang.

32:34.880 --> 32:36.140
They are moving so fast

32:36.310 --> 32:38.310
that they are now less than 20 li
from Xuan River.

32:38.310 --> 32:39.510
The squad is about to cross the river,

32:39.510 --> 32:40.750
so prepare defenses now.

32:40.750 --> 32:42.210
Let there be no oversight.

32:44.060 --> 32:45.060
Did you hear that?

32:45.510 --> 32:47.510
Xiao Wuyi has deployed a troop back.

32:47.750 --> 32:49.110
Since the Beifu Reform began,

32:49.110 --> 32:50.790
unless ordered by the imperial government,

32:50.790 --> 32:53.070
local garrison troops
cannot leave their stations.

32:53.070 --> 32:54.790
This is a military rule
set by Xiao Wuyi himself,

32:54.790 --> 32:55.920
yet he broke it.

32:57.680 --> 32:59.540
Do you still want to plead for him?

33:02.830 --> 33:04.110
Take this secret report

33:04.110 --> 33:06.040
and have a good look at it yourself!

33:24.070 --> 33:25.750
-I want to get out of here!
-There, there.

33:25.750 --> 33:28.310
-Don't cry.
-I want to get out!

33:28.660 --> 33:30.700
I want to get out of this place!

33:30.720 --> 33:33.570
Mom, I want to get out of here!

33:54.040 --> 33:55.720
Don't be afraid. Eat it.

34:00.960 --> 34:01.440
Any findings?

34:01.440 --> 34:03.200
Ye Xing just sent over a message.

34:03.200 --> 34:07.000
The Black Cavalry troop can't be reached
after crossing Xuan River.

34:09.560 --> 34:12.400
The Heir's journey back to the Capital
must be dangerous.

34:12.400 --> 34:14.060
If success can't be guaranteed,

34:14.060 --> 34:14.920
maybe we should

34:14.980 --> 34:15.800
head back to the Northern Border.

34:15.800 --> 34:17.400
Back to the Northern Border?

34:18.440 --> 34:19.570
Then what about Prince Jing'an

34:19.570 --> 34:20.770
and Young Master Yao?

34:21.000 --> 34:22.030
If you're afraid to die,

34:22.030 --> 34:22.710
I'll risk my life.

34:22.710 --> 34:23.230
You...

34:26.000 --> 34:26.860
Your Highness.

34:27.880 --> 34:29.139
They are coming for us.

34:40.840 --> 34:42.670
Mom, I'm scared.

34:43.190 --> 34:44.000
Don't be.

34:44.150 --> 34:45.010
Where are they?

34:50.550 --> 34:51.320
Still haven't

34:51.320 --> 34:52.840
found Xie Jiayu?

34:53.230 --> 34:54.880
General Da has led the Imperial Guard

34:54.880 --> 34:56.610
to search the entire Jiankang,

34:56.760 --> 34:59.020
but found no trace of the Heir's Consort.

34:59.480 --> 35:01.670
As the Beifu Reform
has progressed for two years,

35:01.670 --> 35:03.550
the Imperial Guard has taken
a brand new look,

35:03.550 --> 35:06.010
with the ability to seal the city
like a drum.

35:06.090 --> 35:07.150
But Xie Jiayu still

35:07.960 --> 35:10.280
managed to disappear under our noses.

35:11.360 --> 35:13.070
This means Xie Jiayu, Xiao Wuyi,

35:13.070 --> 35:14.200
and even some others

35:14.510 --> 35:15.710
know a secret escape route

35:15.710 --> 35:17.510
in Jiankang that I am unaware of!

35:17.670 --> 35:18.960
It proves that I still don't

35:18.960 --> 35:21.090
have complete control over Jiankang!

35:22.480 --> 35:24.080
It already happens in a city.

35:24.710 --> 35:26.910
What if it spreads to the whole country?

35:31.030 --> 35:33.430
Xiao Wuyi is back
in Jiankang now, isn't he?

35:34.360 --> 35:35.030
Yes.

35:35.320 --> 35:38.180
Have Jing Lan keep a close watch
on Xiyue Restaurant

35:38.190 --> 35:39.650
and the Miraculous Craft.

35:39.710 --> 35:40.360
Yes.

35:41.710 --> 35:42.360
Careful.

35:44.820 --> 35:46.370
[Xiyue Restaurant]

35:46.470 --> 35:47.870
Xi-Xiyue Restaurant...

35:58.110 --> 35:59.190
Why is a part missing?

35:59.190 --> 36:00.320
This is a Ghost Lamp.

36:00.550 --> 36:01.840
It has a special meaning.

36:01.840 --> 36:03.040
What kind of meaning?

36:03.230 --> 36:04.800
Does it send warning signals or what?

36:04.800 --> 36:05.480
Yes.

36:06.440 --> 36:08.100
It does send warning signals.

36:23.880 --> 36:24.840
Keep drinking!

36:25.710 --> 36:28.000
Tonight, none of us can go home
until we're drunk!

36:28.000 --> 36:28.920
Let's drink!

36:30.880 --> 36:31.920
Come on, let's go.

36:33.630 --> 36:34.090
This...

36:36.400 --> 36:38.630
Xiao Wuyi is cunning and sly.

36:39.800 --> 36:41.000
Even if he's back,

36:41.670 --> 36:44.330
he won't walk right into the trap
by coming here.

36:46.660 --> 36:49.840
[Court of Judicial Review]

36:51.800 --> 36:53.550
So we're
in the Court of Judicial Review now.

36:53.550 --> 36:55.110
This is hardly an accomplishment.

36:55.110 --> 36:56.710
Are Prince Jing'an, Princess Jing'an,

36:56.710 --> 36:58.110
and Xiao Yao all in there?

37:14.190 --> 37:14.840
Yaoyao,

37:15.710 --> 37:16.840
it's time to go home.

37:18.550 --> 37:20.010
You figured I'd come here.

37:20.150 --> 37:21.550
I also figured you'd use Xiao Wuyi

37:21.550 --> 37:22.810
to create a diversion.

37:23.280 --> 37:25.630
What, aren't you afraid I'd catch him?

37:26.400 --> 37:27.730
You wouldn't be able to.

37:27.920 --> 37:28.510
Right.

37:29.630 --> 37:30.890
I did fail to catch him.

37:31.110 --> 37:32.510
He ended up running away.

37:32.670 --> 37:33.470
Nonetheless,

37:33.880 --> 37:37.880
I guessed you'd take this chance
to come rescue his family out of prison.

38:02.800 --> 38:03.360
Run!

38:03.510 --> 38:04.640
Let's go, Madam Liu.

38:05.670 --> 38:07.040
Xiao Wuyi, why did you come here?

38:07.040 --> 38:08.640
I had to, or you can't escape.

38:09.280 --> 38:09.880
Xiao Wuyi,

38:10.070 --> 38:11.330
release His Highness!

38:11.960 --> 38:12.710
Xiao Wuyi,

38:13.670 --> 38:15.190
is this what you call

38:15.830 --> 38:17.870
"being devoted to the country"?

38:20.840 --> 38:23.040
Li Mao, you clearly went way out of line.

38:23.280 --> 38:24.000
You were perfectly aware

38:24.000 --> 38:25.360
that my father was murdered
by Northern Qin,

38:25.360 --> 38:26.550
yet you still seized on it

38:26.550 --> 38:28.060
to take the power over the Beifu Army

38:28.060 --> 38:29.630
and persecute Prince Jing'an's family.

38:29.630 --> 38:31.040
How can you be so unreasonable?

38:31.040 --> 38:32.280
Since when has Jiankang ever been a place

38:32.280 --> 38:33.720
where being reasonable works?

38:33.720 --> 38:35.840
The secret passage you just went through

38:35.840 --> 38:38.190
and the martial masters
hidden in the crowd—

38:38.190 --> 38:38.960
are you keeping them

38:38.960 --> 38:41.090
so you can reason with me in the future?

38:43.760 --> 38:44.510
Xiao Wuyi,

38:45.630 --> 38:47.490
tomorrow is the day of execution.

38:47.940 --> 38:49.540
Even if you can escape death,

38:49.840 --> 38:50.590
those three

38:51.190 --> 38:53.050
family members of yours will not.

38:54.150 --> 38:54.670
Li Mao,

38:56.710 --> 38:58.710
I've been tolerant enough with you.

38:59.360 --> 39:00.420
When we meet again,

39:02.140 --> 39:03.620
I will show you no mercy.

39:09.390 --> 39:10.250
Your Highness!

39:12.940 --> 39:14.200
No need to go after him.

39:15.590 --> 39:18.510
With Prince Jing'an and his other family
in my hands,

39:18.510 --> 39:20.190
he'll surely hurl himself into the net.
